-- LDK Solar in Talks With Strategic Investors, CEO Says in Call
-- B y   R e e d   L a n d b e r g
-- 2012-09-17T12:34:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-17/ldk-solar-in-talks-with-strategic-investors-ceo-says-in-call.html
LDK Solar Co. Chairman Xiaofeng
Peng said he’s in discussions with “two or three” companies
about investing in the Chinese solar-panel manufacturer.  The company, whose second-quarter sales fell 53 percent 
to $235.4 million, also said it’s confident its management 
retains the support of lenders. The executive spoke on a
conference call with investors today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net  